Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:45.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:53.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:56.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:00.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was stuck to my forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:02.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:03.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:05.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Same old Run, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:07.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:08.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:10.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:11.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruuun-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:12.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.15,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, did you see that drama yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:15.53,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:16.66,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:18.97,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about that anime yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:16.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run sure has lots of male friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:17.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure does...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard at work this morning, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:43.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:48.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're small as usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Why are your clothes so dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:41.92,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,And you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.25,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,it wasn't on the map...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me Run was bullying her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:52.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,... chasing a butterfly, and a car was about to hit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite responsible of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:02.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:08.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at lunchtime, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Run-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru! It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:47.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:48.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, come right on over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:07.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of exams and all, we haven't seen each other in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Tooru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:26.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:31.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder... if Run-chan will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I got into the same high school as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:34.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:35.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:38.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, what's with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was she just doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You got in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind getting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the one you wanted to introduce us to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They were announcing the test results today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,and I figured Tooru would stop by,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,so I invited you two over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my friends from our school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan and Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:20.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meetcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together starting spring, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's giving me the death glare...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a bad first impression, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably explain what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:42.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... looks like you misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run was tickling me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't doing anything weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,just fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:50.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they've broken the ice. How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.42,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:39.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sending around the elective sign-up sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like last year's, so you'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our homeroom teacher this year is pretty lax...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:07.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the procedure for filling out your elective selection forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anybody have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,As first-years, you don't have many elective choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:17.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,but your options will increase in later semesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This will affect your future,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,so please think carefully about your choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:25.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any individual questions, please ask at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Run be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch time, lunch time~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:25.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right, it just slipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here, Nagi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:37.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,she heard her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:53.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that squirrel toothpick is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? It's my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I love animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:02.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What's your favorite animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:04.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like parakeets?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, your hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:17.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,looks sorta like a parakeet's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But most of all, they taste so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.14,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Eh? That's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those poor parakeets, being eaten like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what she meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:31.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,always liked to eat chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So your favorite food is a kind of bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! But I like all kinds of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:42.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we go for Korean barbecue sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to have some some grilled ribs and beef tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.37,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really making me crave some Korean barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:55.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if I can already hear the sizzling of barbecuing meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:04.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your ringtone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, your fried eggs look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:12.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, did you make this{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:36.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two sure get along well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's getting along well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good lunch, wasn't it, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:43.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our classroom is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We just moved up grades, so I'm still in the habit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, if you don't hurry up, you'll be late, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Toooooruuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, I see you stayed awake during the afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I was fine all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:13.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did almost falling out of the window wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you should be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:15.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, I'm sleepier in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:20.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some candy to wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.10,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,One for you too, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll save it for Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But then you won't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll split it in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Run, you're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you plan to split that candy in half?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can split it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:11.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be silly if you got hurt over a piece of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:32.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it fell on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:36.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:47.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell like candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You have more?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:18.70,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy! Candy! Candy! Candy! Candy! Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to throw out the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:26.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You could even smell the empty bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause Tooru loves sweet things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:33.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We were eating them earlier, and we finished the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:35.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring more some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want amber candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, how about something a little less sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:42.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,or with less calories...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But the sweet ones taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:48.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, I got it, tomorrow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you two choose as your electives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,As our what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamate-sensei was talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, were you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:04.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so why'd you fall down, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:10.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run looked like she was going to fall over, so I tried to catch her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:14.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,but then she straightened up and I lost my balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.20,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:18.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, what did you put for your first-year electives?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:21.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could take the same classes as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:53.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just too cute, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,S-St-Stop it{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all go out for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:32.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Yuuko! Let me hug her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what's with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run really does have a lot of male friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what they're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:08.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us Yuuko-chan's three sizes, Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:13.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,From the top, 88-56-87.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:17.85,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,... or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:21.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,W-w-why do you know my sizes, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later then, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:26.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:29.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. They all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:42.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:44.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:51.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard at work every morning, huh, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:53.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the candy, just as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat it together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:13.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two really do get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:58.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of candy, there are all sorts of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:24:00.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Drizzles, showers, and gloomy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:02.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know some unusual stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to have a quiz, Miporin!
